{"tid":2091003,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Twitter 戰線一定要堅持！可以將香港現況傳出去","createTime":"2020-07-02T12:55:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-08T04:41:13.000Z","uid":322769,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f9344a47c4e625b02ec53887e1e151e3906a6069","tid":2091003,"uid":322769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T12:55:54.000Z","msg":"好耐之前我post 左張動森入面有抗爭標語既圖 hash tag<br />\n#standwithhongkong<br />\n<br />\n有位記者就好簡單問左我幾條問題<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HVg7cHB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHVg7cHB.png&h=9a15bd49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n尋晚佢再搵我話另一位同事有興趣再做一篇採訪 through email, 問我香港7月1號發生咩事。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X2aG1Bq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX2aG1Bq.png&h=007f4e8b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今朝起身果時已經publish 左係斯德哥爾摩其中一份 major subscription morning paper Svenska Dagbladet<br />\n佢個網同twitter 都有刊登。睇返資料份報紙2017年circulation 有17萬<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m41GhaU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm41GhaU.png&h=30d59ecb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y7811CD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy7811CD.png&h=2028d541&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好多國外媒體都需要當地人去解釋發生緊咩事，每人每日係Twitter 簡單retweet 幾個，回幾個tweet 已經幫到好多。"},{"pid":"362c5e19c79369363ebef9706e9f459e658e596f","tid":2091003,"uid":24862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T00:21:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ea91470d2a313a255d70d2e526a491a12bcadbf","tid":2091003,"uid":289861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T00:24:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cc0074c6f629eba0e93772968c36998e6978adf